v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng ch\u00e1y hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-6709\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/rem-la-doc-rpt2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1536\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/rem-la-doc-rpt2.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/rem-la-doc-rpt2-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/rem-la-doc-rpt2-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/rem-la-doc-rpt2-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/rem-la-doc-rpt2-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/rem-la-doc-rpt2-510x383.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080;\">3. \u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m l\u00e1 d\u1ecdc<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-6710\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/rem-la-doc-rpt3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/rem-la-doc-rpt3.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/rem-la-doc-rpt3-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/rem-la-doc-rpt3-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/rem-la-doc-rpt3-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/rem-la-doc-rpt3-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/rem-la-doc-rpt3-2048x1536.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/rem-la-doc-rpt3-510x383.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #333399;\">* C\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec7t t\u1ed1t<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<p>M\u00e0nh r\u00e8m l\u00e1 d\u1ecdc c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ea3n s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t<\/p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #333399;\">* M\u1ed7i lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m l\u00e1 d\u1ecdc c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng kh\u00e1c nhau<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<p>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xoay l\u1eadt ph\u1ea3i\/tr\u00e1i 180 \u0111\u1ed9, k\u00e9o d\u1ea1t h\u1ebft sang 1 b\u00ean ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ec1u 2 b\u00ean gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng cho c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng che n\u1eafng t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u (c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u00e0n t\u1eeb \u00dac c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3n s\u00e1ng 100%). Ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c nhau s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng kh\u00e1c nhau c\u1ee7a m\u00e0nh l\u1eadt. \u0110a ph\u1ea7n c\u00e1c m\u1eabu m\u00e0nh l\u00e1 d\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng gian<\/p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #333399;\">* R\u00e8m l\u00e1 d\u1ecdc c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1ec7 sinh<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<p>R\u00e8m l\u00e1 d\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ebf t\u1ea1o b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1ec7 sinh khi b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, c\u00e1c b\u1ea3n l\u00e1 d\u1ecdc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c treo tr\u00ean thanh \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1ec7 sinh b\u1eb1ng kh\u0103n lau \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, ho\u1eb7c lau nh\u1eb9 b\u1eb1ng v\u1ea3i \u1ea5m, ho\u1eb7c n\u1ebfu r\u00e8m l\u00e1 d\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eafp \u1edf c\u00e1c \u00f4 c\u1eeda l\u1edbn, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1ec7 sinh b\u1eb1ng m\u00e1y h\u00fat b\u1ee5i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng<\/p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #333399;\">* V\u1eadt li\u1ec7u c\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7t t\u1ed1t\u00a0<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<p>R\u00e8m l\u00e1 d\u1ecdc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t r\u00e0o c\u1ea3n l\u1edbn t\u1eeb s\u1ee9c n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u00e0 gi\u1eef cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 ho\u1eb7c v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n m\u00e1t m\u1ebb. R\u00e8m c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m t\u00e1c h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tia UV c\u00f3 h\u1ea1i t\u1eeb m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t trong nh\u00e0 ho\u1eb7c n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng ty. V\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng, r\u00e8m l\u00e1 d\u1ecdc c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i \u00edch k\u00e9p l\u00e0 gi\u00fap gi\u1eef nhi\u1ec7t, v\u00ec n\u00f3 tho\u00e1t ra \u00edt h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080;\">5. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t r\u00e8m l\u00e1 d\u1ecdc \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u cho h\u1ee3p l\u00fd nh\u1ea5t<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>R\u00e8m l\u00e1 d\u1ecdc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eafp \u1edf m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng gian nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf l\u1eafp \u1edf kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7. R\u00e8m l\u00e1 d\u1ecdc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 khi l\u1eafp \u1edf m\u1ecdi kh\u00f4ng gian. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi c\u00f4ng r\u00e8m l\u00e1 d\u1ecdc \u1edf ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch, ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp, \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng, h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, gi\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng \u0103n, hay trung t\u00e2m th\u0